Issue id requires for this request, so please fill out it.

A.Is possible. You can create a test destination group beforehand and send tests to the group you created. For more details  
[Click here!](https://confluence.rakuten-it.com/confluence/display/FELIX/User+Manual+-+Test+Contacts+Groups 'link')

Q.What is Open measurement method?  
A.Opens can be tracked in HTML emails because they include a tracking pixel, which is a tiny, invisible image, that is displayed when the subscriber opens your email. When that image is downloaded from our web servers, the email is recorded as being opened.
